bler&rsquo;s fallacy 係種謬誤 <br />\n<br />\n係咪啫係有矛盾？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T16:46:47.000Z","msg":"頭盔：唔係stat撚，有錯請指正<br />\n<br />\nBayesian個中心思想係，未有data既情況下，概率只係描述緊你對某件事既信心，而當你開始獲得data，你就可以用佢黎update你對呢件事既信心<br />\n<br />\n同傳統既概率(&ldquo;frequentist&rdquo; probability)最唔同既地方係，傳統概率假設左某件事已經確定左概率，當你做好多次實驗就可以用「發生次數/實驗次數」黎estimate呢個已經確定左既概率，而Bayes主張唔存在呢一個「已經確定左概率」，所有概率只係描越緊你既信心<br />\n<br />\n例如你認為擲公字既概率係50-50，呢個就係你最初既信念(&ldquo;prior&rdquo; probability)<br />\nBayesian既做法係用實驗data去update呢個50-50既信念(Bayes&rsquo; theorem)，然後計出一個介乎50-50同「擲中公既次數次數/實驗次數」之間既概率(&ldquo;posterior&rdquo; probability)<br />\n而frequentist做法係assume背後有一個已經確定既概率，然後用不同方法去處理data，從而estimate呢個「已經確定既概率」係幾多"},{"pid":"6f777d06be24a47a53d2ca176ceff7832dfeca4c","tid":2389072,"uid":3441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T17:03:38.000Z","msg":"Independence is rather an assumption of your model.<br />\nTo check the validity of assumption of independence there're various statistical tests in different situations."},{"pid":"2c5bf95f10610dc48a049ebfff2a0edb365ba9a7","tid":2389072,"uid":80303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ca8a3cd8eee35e77e29a509559cd3917dba49ab4","tid":2389072,"uid":22302,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"c21fddbd3cf5316d4b31dcad926f3772f5b1ebbd","tid":2389072,"uid":104210,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"4c80c3360d86882f3b3604926b4e818670059672","tid":2389072,"uid":22302,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T15:09:12.000Z","msg":"google Bayesian inference"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T16:19:26.000Z","msg":"唔知有無理解錯 呢個推論係指出可以用past experimental data嚟做之後嘅假設？<br />\n<br />\n但係上面又有巴打講話呢種係gambler&rsquo;s fallacy 係種謬誤 <br />\n<br />\n係咪啫係有矛盾？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T16:46:47.000Z","msg":"頭盔：唔係stat撚，有錯請指正<br />\n<br />\nBayesian個中心思想係，未有data既情況下，概率只係描述緊你對某件事既信心，而當你開始獲得data，你就可以用佢黎update你對呢件事既信心<br />\n<br />\n同傳統既概率(&ldquo;frequentist&rdquo; probability)最唔同既地方係，傳統概率假設左某件事已經確定左概率，當你做好多次實驗就可以用「發生次數/實驗次數」黎estimate呢個已經確定左既概率，而Bayes主張唔存在呢一個「已經確定左概率」，所有概率只係描越緊你既信心<br />\n<br />\n例如你認為擲公字既概率係50-50，呢個就係你最初既信念(&ldquo;prior&rdquo; probability)<br />\nBayesian既做法係用實驗data去update呢個50-50既信念(Bayes&rsquo; theorem)，然後計出一個介乎50-50同「擲中公既次數次數/實驗次數」之間既概率(&ldquo;posterior&rdquo; probability)<br />\n而frequentist做法係assume背後有一個已經確定既概率，然後用不同方法去處理data，從而estimate呢個「已經確定既概率」係幾多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T20:43:38.000Z","msg":"正解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBayesian 同 frequenist 個世界觀有差別<br />\n冇話邊個啱啲"},{"pid":"44da251f9c5cafcef57d5a6221377f55dea602e2","tid":2389072,"uid":80303,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T20:44:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/20587681\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zhihu.com%2Fquestion%2F20587681&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1G8F4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=1ace98a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.zhihu.com/question/20587681</a><br />\n<br />\n贝叶斯学派与频率学派有何不同？-知乎"},{"pid":"2ec0fe866d3e97e9e619150335f1b8dc1e7aa4f7","tid":2389072,"uid":361966,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"de76003e1c1498e18c386b1d8db753bbf1c0dae3","tid":2389072,"uid":136590,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T15:40:08.000Z","msg":"呢個mindset係gambler's fallacy<br />\n如果你一開始assume每次擲骰都係indepedent<br />\n咁無論你之前開咗幾多鋪 佢地嘅結果都唔會影響依家開嘅呢一鋪<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gambler%27s_fallacy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FGambler%2527s_fallacy&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1G8F4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=0d49f52b\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gambler%27s_fallacy</a><br />\n<br />\n當然 實際到你擲嗰時係咪真係independent就另一回事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T20:46:47.000Z","msg":"你可以argue粒骰唔係fair dice<br />\n否則佢只要假設indepedent<br />\n咁你點都係1／2"},{"pid":"d7b75c9a423b73e3f85bb8f0d333f504f88ec023","tid":2389072,"uid":302117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco